64
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:14,497
He’ll be back to normal soon, I’m sure.

65
00:05:16,739 --> 00:05:18,959
Well, Phaad!

66
00:05:19,109 --> 00:05:22,603
Good thing we have Phun around.

67
00:05:23,755 --> 00:05:25,546
She’s been such a help to me.

68
00:05:26,015 --> 00:05:28,437
Say, Phun, what if someday

69
00:05:28,686 --> 00:05:30,719
your folks come to redeem you?

70
00:05:30,957 --> 00:05:35,453
I’d be so lonely without you.

71
00:05:36,501 --> 00:05:38,604
I won’t leave, Mae Samorn.

72
00:05:38,871 --> 00:05:43,274
If you’re kind to me, I will stay and serve you.

73
00:05:43,378 --> 00:05:45,383
And stay by P'Phaad’s side forever too.

74
00:05:46,970 --> 00:05:48,674
